## API Endpoints Summary

### Authentication
- `POST /api/login/` - User authentication
- `GET /api/current_user/` - Get current user info
- `POST /api/register/` - User registration

### Admin Dashboard
- `GET /api/dashboard/` - Dashboard statistics
- `GET /api/admin/analytics/` - Comprehensive analytics
- `GET /api/recent-activities/` - Recent system activities

### User Management
- `GET /api/admin-users/` - List all users (admin only)
- `POST /api/admin-users/{id}/toggle_status/` - Toggle user status
- `POST /api/admin-users/{id}/reset_password/` - Reset user password
- `POST /api/admin-users/{id}/update_role/` - Update user role
- `GET /api/admin-users/statistics/` - User statistics

### Book Management
- `GET /api/admin-books/` - List all books (admin only)
- `POST /api/admin-books/{id}/increment_views/` - Increment book views
- `POST /api/admin-books/{id}/toggle_featured/` - Toggle featured status
- `GET /api/admin-books/statistics/` - Book statistics

### System Health
- `GET /api/admin/system-health/` - System health monitoring
- `GET /api/admin/user-activity/` - User activity monitoring
- `POST /api/admin/bulk-operation/` - Bulk administrative operations

