```

## Usage Instructions

### For Administrators
1. Login with admin credentials
2. Access `/admin` route for admin dashboard
3. Use sidebar navigation to access different sections
4. Perform bulk operations using checkboxes and action buttons
5. Monitor system health and analytics from dashboard

### For Staff Members
1. Login with staff credentials
2. Access appropriate admin sections based on permissions
3. Manage assigned content and users
4. Monitor activities and performance metrics

### API Usage
1. Obtain JWT token through login endpoint
2. Use token in Authorization header for admin endpoints
3. All admin endpoints require appropriate permissions
4. Use bulk operations for efficient data management

